Local
> https://www.mongodb.com/try/download/community
> in c drive create one folder by the name of data
> inside data create folder name db 
> c:/data/db

# 1st Cmd  (start mongodb server)
-----------------
> open cmd 
> go inside mongodb folder
> cd c:/program/mongodb/server/4.4/bin (go to the bin folder with cmd )
> type mongod 
> it will start mongodb server on port 27017

#2nd Cmd (start mongodb console)
-------------
> go inside mongodb bin folder
> type mongo

